children.text:
The GCF of $32x^3$, $-4x^2$, and $20x$ is $8x$. We factor $8x$ out of each term to get \begin{align*}
32x^3-4x^2+20x &= 8x\cdot4x^2 - 8x\cdot 1 + 8x\cdot 5\\
&= \boxed{8x(4x^2-1+5)}.
\end{align*}

